sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Buyer
    participant S as Seller
    participant N as Nevermined

    B->>S: 1. POST /ask (no token)
    S-->>B: 2. 402 + payment-required

    B->>N: 3. Request x402 token
    N-->>B: 4. Access token

    B->>S: 5. POST /ask + payment-signature
    S->>N: 6. Verify
    N-->>S: 7. Valid ✓
    Note over S: Business logic
    S->>N: 8. Settle
    N-->>S: 9. Receipt
    S-->>B: 10. 200 + payment-response
